stickers.name: amiya_yay
stickers.alt: Amiya holds her arms out as she beams.

stickers.name: amiya_tasty
stickers.alt: Amiya happily licks her lips after eating something tasty. She holds up a spoon in her left hand where the tasty stuff presumably was.

stickers.name: angelina_cup
stickers.alt: Angelina pokes her head out of a cup of yogurt with a wooden spoon handle sticking out. Her hands hold onto the edge of the cup as she tilts her head and gives the viewer a confused look.

stickers.name: angelina_heart
stickers.alt: Angelina winks at the viewer as she creates a heart shape with her hands.

stickers.name: saria_command
stickers.alt: Saria holds up a bowl of rice in her left hand and has her right hand on her hip. There's a threatening shadow over her face as she seems to make a demand.

stickers.name: saria_scoop
stickers.alt: Saria pats a fresh scoop of rice from the rice cooker into a serving bowl.

stickers.name: lapp_snack
stickers.alt: Lappland props up her head on her left elbow as she eats what looks like a yellow and red eraser in her right hand.

stickers.name: lapp_utensil
stickers.alt: Lappland menacingly holds an oversized knife in her right hand and an oversized fork in her left hand, ready to eat.

stickers.name: exe_surprise
stickers.alt: Executor holds up a cupcake in his right hand, only to be surprised as he discovered a plus-shaped cookie to be tasty.

stickers.name: exe_abandon
stickers.alt: Executor eats a plus shaped cookie, turning his back on a cupcake that is now sulking in the corner.

stickers.name: greythroat_emptyhanded
stickers.alt: GreyThroat keeps a spoon in her mouth with her left hand while her right shows it being empty-handed.

stickers.name: greythroat_fork
stickers.alt: GreyThroat holds an oversized and long fork in her hand like it's a lance while walking. There's a cup on her with head with the image of a carrot on the lid.

stickers.name: beagle_slice
stickers.alt: Beagle takes a bite of a pizza slice, struggling with the cheese pull.

stickers.name: beagle_pizza
stickers.alt: Beagle opens a pizza box with a wagging tail, excitedly showing off the pizza within.

stickers.name: midnight_cone
stickers.alt: Midnight tries to be suave like he's in a shoujo anime, flowers and sparkles in the background. He holds out a cone of ice cream to the viewer with his left hand, eyes closed, and his right hand making some sort of pose to make him seem cool.

stickers.name: midnight_icecream
stickers.alt: Midnight grins as he holds up an ice cream cone that is nearly twice his height, showing it off as shoujo sparkles appear around him.
